<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <title>Password successfully reset</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello, {{name}}</h1>
    <p>Recently, a request to reset your password was made for your account.</p>
    <p>If you requested this password reset, please click on the link below to
      proceed.</p>
    <p><a href='{{resetUrl}}'>Verify</a></p>
    <p>The link will expire in {{expirationInHours}} hours.</p>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset link, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>KANTT</p>
  </body>
</html>